== Changelog


=== Release 3.4.1 (Aug 16, 2011)

= FEATURES

* None

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Modified the Server WSUS sync script to use the new WSUS server


=== Release 3.4.1 (June 19, 2011)

= FEATURES

* None

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* The Salad now queries the FDC vCenter Database in addition to the existing IDC one


=== Release 3.4  (June 8, 2011)

= FEATURES

* PC Health - Evaluates each PC and assigns a Health status based on acquired data

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Win 7 and Server 2008 OS detection
* Properly functioning 64 bit Server OS detection
* BalancePoint sync moved to PS-BalancePoint.mis.local
* Removed SCCM Configuration Issue requirement from Rules


=== Release 3.3  (April 18, 2011)

= FEATURES

* Avamar data added to Server details display
* OU information collected and displayed

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Added AD Last Logon Timestamp to PC updates collection
* Corrected calculation for PC Most Recent Update


=== Release 3.2.1  (February 8, 2011)

= FEATURES

* None

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Fixed tooltip bug not keeping tips onscreen at all times
* Fixed IE7 javascript issues preventing any tooltips from appearing


=== Release 3.2.0  (February 2, 2011)

= FEATURES

* Fully redesigned Server and PC details display

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Added NewRelic RPM monitoring
* Updated Hoptoad exception monitoring


=== Release 3.1.1  (January 24, 2011)

= FEATURES

* None

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* WSUS patch collection queries all groups individually


=== Release 3.1.0  (December 1, 2010)

= FEATURES

* PCs view is fully functional

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Additional WSUS and EPO information available on the compliance view
* SCCM Sync looks in additional OUs for Servers
* PC Sync scripts production ready


=== Release 3.0.0  (June 14, 2010)

= FEATURES

* All alerts are now imported from SCOM and display on hover
* Server health is now determined based on a set of compliance rules

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* In modern browsers, tooltips function significantly better than before
* Added sorting by Owner
* Changed the ePO import script to be more reliable
* Previous day SCOM Uptime is now displayed on the Default view


=== Release 2.3.0  (April 30, 2010)

= FEATURES

* Assigned owners and server descriptions can be modified from the list view
* Broke server "Production" status into three Tiers
* Server status is automatically assigned based on SCOM group membership
* Added ILC as a company option

= FIXES / ENHANCEMENTS

* Removed SCOM's ability to create new owners
* Updated DC list for RMR's 2008 R2 project
* Updated SCOM query with NOLOCKs
* Enhanced Avamar query to exclude inactive
* Correct physical/virtual identification thus improving views
* Hacked the prototype controls.js file extensively for better inplaceediting compatibility